ZH: 雪花飘落在窗外。
EN: Snowflakes are falling outside the window.

ZH: 雪山上有许多野生动物。
EN: There are many wild animals on the snowy mountain.

ZH: 我们度假时看到了一场大雪。
EN: We saw a heavy snowfall during our vacation.

ZH: 雪地上有许多留下的动物脚印。
EN: There are many animal footprints left in the snow.

ZH: 昨晚下了很大的雪。
EN: It snowed heavily last night.

ZH: 雪层越来越厚。
EN: The snow layer is getting thicker.

ZH: 小孩们在雪地里堆雪人。
EN: Children are building a snowman in the snow.

ZH: 冬天是观赏雪景的好时机。
EN: Winter is a good time to appreciate snowy scenes.

ZH: 我们可以用雪板在雪地里滑行。
EN: We can snowboard in the snow.

ZH: 雪花飘飘，如梦如幻。
EN: Snowflakes are falling like a dream.

ZH: 雪白的山峰在太阳下闪耀。
EN: The snowy peaks are shining in the sun.

ZH: 雪球在手中变成水。
EN: The snowball turns into water in your hand.

ZH: 他们在雪地里迷路了。
EN: They got lost in the snow.

ZH: 雪景如诗如画。
EN: The snowy scene is picturesque.

ZH: 我喜欢看雪花飘落的感觉。
EN: I like the feeling of watching snowflakes fall.

ZH: 雪后一尘不染的世界是如此美丽。
EN: The world after the snow is so beautifully spotless.

ZH: 雪地上有一只小小的兔子。
EN: There is a tiny rabbit on the snow.

ZH: 雪后的清晨空气特别清新。
EN: The air is especially fresh on the morning after snow.

ZH: 雪花纷飞，宛如仙境。
EN: Snowflakes flutter down as if in a fairyland.

ZH: 那天下了一场大雪，我们都感到惊讶。
EN: We were all surprised by the heavy snow that day.
